description: TEHRAN - On Thursday, the commander of the Islamic Revolution Guards Corps (IRGC) Navy reaffirmed Iran's unwavering stance on defending its sovereignty, warning that any aggressor attempting to infringe upon it will have "their leg broken and their wrong eye blinded."
title: IRGC: 'We will blind the wrong eye of any aggressor'

description: TEHRAN - Following a confirmation by the Lebanese Hezbollah resistance movement on Wednesday that Sayyid Hashem Safieddine, the head of Hezbollah's Executive Council, has been martyred in the Israeli massive bombardments of Beirut, Leader of the Islamic Revolution Ayatollah Ali Khamenei issued a message on Thursday asserting that “Hezbollah is alive, thriving, and fulfilling its historic role.”
title: Hezbollah thriving and fulfilling its historic role, Leader says of Safieddine martyrdom

description: TEHRAN – Iran remained unchanged in 19th in the last FIFA Ranking update released on Thursday.
title: Iran unchanged in FIFA ranking

description: TEHRAN - Iran Greco-Roman wrestling team won the title of the 2024 U23 World Championships in Tirana, Albania Wednesday night.
title: Iran Greco-Roman crowned champions of 2024 U23 World

description: TEHRAN – DPR Korea made it three wins out of three with a 4-1 defeat of Iran in the AFC U17 Asian Cup Saudi Arabia 2025.
title: DPR Korea too strong for Iran in AFC U17 Asian Cup 2025 qualifiers
